<P>> I have strong beliefs that it is very unfair. what i mean by

<BR>&gt; this is that on the PvP server it is almost impossible for a
<BR>&gt; warrior 2 survive when being attacked by an equal level wizard
<BR>&gt; or something else with those high (80) dam spells. Well i think
<BR>&gt; that u should put in special armor that only warriors may wear
<BR>&gt; that help them lik +5 to resist all or some armor that onlyu
<BR>&gt; warriors get, that would somehow even out the fights.
<P>I agree with you, with the present armor wizards have a major advantage because in 2 or 3 spells they can kill even a heavily armored warrior (or shadowknight) we need armor that helps the warrior classes deal with that huge damage.
